'''''Old [[गोंय|Goa]]n Gold''''' zaun asa [[Remo Fernandes]]achem 1985 vorsak bhair kadlelem ek kantarancho ''album''. Hantunt [[Konknni]] ani [[Portuguez bhas|Portuguez]] bhasani kantaram asat. Alisha Chinain-ui hea albuman gailam.

Ho albuman kantaram asat jeo Remo vadtana radvocher ani aplem paiche ''gramophone-ar'' aikotalo. Ho album poilo ''cassette''-ancher bhair kadlolo, hacho ek ''side'' Konknnint asli, zalear dusri side Portuguezint.<ref name="goanvoice">[http://www.goanvoice.org.uk/supplement/RemoFernandes.html [[गोंय|Goa]]n Voice UK: supplement on Remo Fernandes<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

Hea albumant adleo kantaram asat ani char noveo kantaram asleot, tin Konknnint ani ek Portuguezint. Noveo kantaram asat: [[mando]] 'Panch Vorsam' (Alisha ani Remon gailolem ani Remon rochlelem ''Trikaal'', hem Hindi cholchitrak, 'Soiri', 'Konknni' ([[Konkani language agitation]] hachem gaion), ani ' ''Fado [[गोंय|Goa]]'' '<ref name="goanvoice" />. 'Soiri' zaun aslem Dr. [[Manohar Rai Sardesai]]n boroil'li kovita.

Hea albuman Remon soglleo ''instrument'' vazoile ani soglle avanchim kantaram-ui svotaun kelem (Alishan gailele kantaram sodun). Muzk ani utram-ui Remonuch boroilim ani ''recording''-ui tenen uch kelem. Albumacho kovor legun Remonuch rochle.<ref>[http://www.goa-world.com/goa/music/remo.htm GOA WORLD - Music - Remo Fernandes<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

